            "modalityName": "6-hour tour",
            "contentId": "61394",
            "description": "If you want<strong> to get to know Paris in the most comfortable and personal way,</strong> with a guide at your complete disposal, come with us to discover the most interesting corners of the city.<br />\nThe guide will make <strong>an itinerary based on your tastes and preferences.</strong><br />\n<br />\nWe will <strong>discover Paris quietly</strong>, with time to take photos, buy souvenirs and have lunch in a restaurant of your choice. It will be a unique tour in which our guide will also tell you details and curiosities about local Parisian life.<br />\n<br />\nIn our standard itinerary we will see the most important monuments and attractions of Paris: Notre Dame Cathedral, Latin Quarter, Seine River, Pont Neuf, Pont des Arts, Louvre Museum pyramid, Opéra Garnier, Tuileries Garden, Champs Elysées, Arc de Triomphe, Pont Alexandre III, Eiffel Tower, Île de la Cité, Place Vendôme, Montmartre, Sacré-Coeur Basilica, Moulin Rouge...<br />\n<quillbot-extension-portal></quillbot-extension-portal><quillbot-extension-portal></quillbot-extension-portal>",
